  "statement": {
    "markdown": "Given an array of integers `nums` and an integer `k`, return the number of contiguous subarrays where the sum of the elements equals `k`. The subarray should have at least one element and all elements must be in `nums`. The array `nums` can contain both positive and negative integers.",
